SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ORGANIZATION'S FUND MANAGER IS ALSO THE FUND MANAGER OF TWO OTHER ENTITIES AND AN OFFICER FOR THE RELATED LOCAL UNION.
